    # "For now, I should go see Adrian."
    "Por agora, tenho de ir ver a Adrian."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:5
translate portuguese u20j_33260fe1:

    # "I drive over to Adrian's house and ring the doorbell."
    "Dirijo-me até à casa da Adrian e toco à campainha."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:6
translate portuguese u20j_4fc89239:

    # "It's late and I hate to wake her, but I need to see her."
    "É tarde e detesto acordá-la, mas preciso de a ver."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:9
translate portuguese u20j_494a3331:

    # "Adrian's Mom" "Hello? Do you know how late it is?"
    "Adrian's Mom" "Estás aí? Sabes que horas são?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:10
translate portuguese u20j_7d43c485:

    # pc "I'm sorry, I know. I'm a friend of Adrian's."
    pc "Desculpa, eu sei. Sou um amigo da Adrian."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:11
translate portuguese u20j_87309e2a:

    # pc "Could I talk to her, please?"
    pc "Posso falar com ela, por favor?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:12
translate portuguese u20j_ad012933:

    # "Adrian's Mom" "Oh, are you [pcname]? She's been worried about you for weeks."
    "Adrian's Mom" "Ah, é o [pcname]? Ela está preocupada consigo há semanas."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:13
translate portuguese u20j_332de7e5:

    # pc "Yes, I'm sorry. That's me."
    pc "Sim, desculpe. Sou eu."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:16
translate portuguese u20j_1a0d366a:

    # "Adrian's Mom" "She's going to be really happy to see you."
    "Adrian's Mom" "Ela vai ficar muito feliz por vê-lo."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:17
translate portuguese u20j_1108c1b8:

    # "Adrian's Mom" "You can go up and see her, just keep things PG, okay?"
    "Adrian's Mom" "Pode subir e vê-la, mas mantenha a conversa adequada para todas as idades, está bem?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:18
translate portuguese u20j_e170ff6c:

    # pc "Yes, ma'am. Thank you."
    pc "Sim, senhora. Obrigado."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:22
translate portuguese u20j_f5638052:

    # "I walk quietly up the stairs and into Adrian's room. She's in bed, sleeping."
    "Subo as escadas em silêncio e entro no quarto da Adrian. Ela está na cama, a dormir."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:25
translate portuguese u20j_cbba5bfa:

    # "Trying not to wake her immediately, I lie next to her and wrap my arms around her."
    "Tentando não a acordar de imediato, deito-me ao lado dela e envolvo-a nos meus braços."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:28
translate portuguese u20j_c981bd85:

    # "She jolts awake and looks at me, shocked."
    "Ela acorda de sobressalto e olha para mim, chocada."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:29
translate portuguese u20j_a857ee55:

    # gg "What the fuck? [pcname]?"
    gg "Que raio? [pcname]?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:32
translate portuguese u20j_0f0952fe:

    # "I don't answer. I just pull her close and kiss her deeply."
    "Não respondo. Apenas a puxo para perto de mim e beijo-a profundamente."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:33
translate portuguese u20j_09b23034:

    # gg "Fuck, I was so worried about you. I thought you weren't ever coming back."
    gg "Raios, estava tão preocupada contigo. Pensei que nunca mais voltasses."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:36
translate portuguese u20j_b1adfb65:

    # gg "So you went to another world, for real?"
    gg "Então foste para outro mundo, a sério?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:37
translate portuguese u20j_e5f2498c:

    # pc "Yeah, I did."
    pc "Sim, fui."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:38
translate portuguese u20j_29a8b357:

    # gg "And you saw your dad?"
    gg "E viste o teu pai?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:39
translate portuguese u20j_c417e350:

    # pc "Yeah."
    pc "Sim."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:40
translate portuguese u20j_fa6e7016:

    # gg "You have to tell me everything."
    gg "Tens de me contar tudo."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:41
translate portuguese u20j_0bb899f2:

    # pc "I will, I promise. Tomorrow."
    pc "Vou contar, prometo. Amanhã."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:44
translate portuguese u20j_92c42e64:

    # gg "Right. Tomorrow. I'm just glad you're back!"
    gg "Certo. Amanhã. Só estou feliz por estares de volta!"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:45
translate portuguese u20j_d2639c3b:

    # gg "I can't believe you're back."
    gg "Não acredito que estás de volta."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:46
translate portuguese u20j_c01c395d:

    # gg "I'm so happy, I can't stand it."
    gg "Estou tão feliz que nem consigo aguentar."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:49
translate portuguese u20j_f432b969:

    # "I pull her close and kiss her again, feeling her warmth."
    "Puxo-a para perto de mim e beijo-a novamente, sentindo o seu calor."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:50
translate portuguese u20j_bf4f63bf:

    # gg "Good idea. Shut me up with your mouth."
    gg "Boa ideia. Cala-me com a tua boca."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:51
translate portuguese u20j_1530bf0e:

    # gg "I just missed you so much."
    gg "Senti tanto a tua falta."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20j.rpy:52
translate portuguese u20j_9c24a5ca:

    # pc "I missed you too, Adrian."
    pc "Também senti a tua falta, Adrian."

